%N A395706 Expansion of g^6*(4*g-3)/(5-4*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^5 is the g.f. of A002294.
%F A395706 a(n) = (n+1) * A386367(n+1).
%F A395706 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (8*k+3)/(5*k+3) * binomial(5*k+3,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(5*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395706 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/5) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(5*k,k) * x^k ).
%F A395706 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(5*k+3+l,k) * binomial(5*n-5*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395706 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 4^(n-k) * binomial(5*n+4,k).
%F A395706 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 5^(n-k) * binomial(4*n+k+3,k).
%o A395706 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 4^(n-k)*binomial(5*n+4, k));
